      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "fb_china_today",
        "uid": "8633"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t锁链女也一样<br/>\n“没办法” “这辈子就这样了”<br/>\n<br/>\n你看河南那对小夫妇大概就是这种意思\t\t</div>",
